Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this is where we sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens next?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The shadow knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the shadow knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What evil lies in the hearts of men?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The shadow knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Randy Langston.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to take your journal, the Orthomolecular Psychiatry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I practiced ENT and allergy years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about, you know, if I have strong opinions about something and then trying to calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, say political parties, if Franklin Pierce were running and I had strong opinions about Franklin Pierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that affect the ability to calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It would unless you're pretty sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A few people are really capable of being sufficiently detached that they really want to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you can do, like in, let's say, politics you're bringing up, is you calibrate the people they hang out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Birds of a feather flock together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you calibrate who do they hang out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will give you the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because groups usually calibrate around the same, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're either above 200 or below 200, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So if somebody hangs out, if their closest associates over the years have all been members of the mafia, you don't have to really calibrate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You just know the general area in which, you know, this person is aligned, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But becoming detached, there's a way we do it sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is we'll write that thing down and put it in an envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll say the name I have in the envelope stands for somebody who calibrates so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm not influencing her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can do it blind like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to be detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It really takes a scientific education.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The scientist is only interested in the answer to the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have any invested interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And what the answer is, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's one way around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when it comes to politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very hard for people to be detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Very hard to be detached there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's connected to so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your childhood, your culture, the world you grew up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I grew up, you know, in World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So the world I grew up in, the depression was already on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of Prohibition came.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you made money running a little booze out to the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not considered to be, you know, anything bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a little bathtub gin, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are probably a lot of people that would consider that horrible, you know, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That answers it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Making bathtub gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather was good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Juniper berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm putting juniper berries in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You got.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that was a different era.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I signing it in the right place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Derek or Penn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that book?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What version is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the Lamb's Survival or the?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Eastern Text.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Lamb's Survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's from the Lamb's Survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That calibrates higher than the King James Version.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,King James Version is from the Greek.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lamb's Survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from the Eastern Manuscripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never calibrated anyone or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have great curiosity about learning how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have read your descriptions of how to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but my question really centers around finding someone with whom I can practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sometimes a problem to find somebody that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can practice with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:05:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In a group like this, there's lots of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually there's groups that are curious about it and interested in practice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest you do it blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, what I'm holding in mind calibrates over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing you want to know is that over or under 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if it's over, then you're, you know, levels of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What level of truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's under 200, then you know it's not truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So the main thing you want to know is that over or under 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the main thing you want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And it should not be too difficult to find somebody who will go weak when they picture the devil
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and go strong when they picture an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of my concern is that I may not calibrate over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't have to calibrate over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,To be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're interested in truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,People under 200 are not interested in truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're interested in propagating what they believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask with the arm something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's capable of learning the technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, you know, you wouldn't be interested otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,People are not interested in the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to find out, how do you find out the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I signing these right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I did with the right pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I had it ready for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My only question is, I wanted to ask you for a blessing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:07:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a blessing because you're spiritually aligned, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to be means that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I certainly feel no, I certainly bless your spirituality and corroborate it and pledge it to the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dedicate your spiritual awareness to the highest good that it serves not only yourself, but your fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because every time you, because when your level of consciousness goes up, it benefits all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say when you're, the level of the sea goes up, it lifts all the ships at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Be all that you can be out of your love, love for mankind and love for God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And that gives it even more power, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:07:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dedicate your spiritual awareness for the goodness of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And the relief of suffering of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that microphone working okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everybody hearing everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, I used visualization for a long time to try to achieve my goals in the everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's used visualization in his trying to achieve his goals in everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Visualize what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Visualize what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wish for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I learned your teachings and I gave it almost completely up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly enough, my life did not collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is wrong with the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Echo back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So I gave it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,See what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question raised, how to find balance between the willingness to achieve the goals
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in everyday life and between the willingness to accept the evolution of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you balance between what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual evolution and?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Practical?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And the practical goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Practical world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you see them as different?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:10:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm a surgeon, I ask God to help me to be the best surgeon I can possibly be for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the good of the patient and everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if I end up being a better surgeon, then it benefits me indirectly because everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,says, you know, I hear he's a very good surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,See, but you don't do it so that everybody thinks you're a great surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it because of the excellence of your dedication to what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I'm selling vacuum cleaners from house to house, I pray to be able to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, as many vacuum cleaners as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to be the best you can be at whatever you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask to be the best you can be at that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The best you can be at whatever you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:10:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My question for you today is one that's been bothering me, or I've had for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is when Jesus said that no one comes to the Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No one comes to the Father but by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you go somewhere by someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly did he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus, if you, if Jesus Christ is your teacher, your ultimate teacher, then he is your, he
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,says, in return, I will become your advocate before the Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I will speak for you as an advocate before the Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ calibrated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that would be a very powerful friend in Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:11:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he vouches for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I vouch to the degree that any error I have taught, I will speak before the Father that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I taught you incorrectly, that I stand by the truth of what I teach to the best of my
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,knowledge, and that I will attest to the Lord that I have spoken to you correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I will speak to the Lord that I have spoken to you correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I will speak to the Lord that I have spoken to you correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will speak to the Lord that I have spoken incorrectly to them, and I will speak in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,your behalf so that I make that pledge to you as a teacher, and I will take responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that I incorrectly informed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I will speak for you in the celestial realm, or something, the Buddha of, something land,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of Buddha, of, yes, yes, who functions the same as Jesus Christ, but in the Buddha realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any downside to not looking at the id?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In therapy, sometimes, you know, you ask questions, and then you really look at the dark side
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of the id.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any downside to not looking at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any downside to not looking at the id?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To not looking at the id?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In therapy, sometimes, you know, you ask, well, how does that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the id sort of comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any harm in looking at the id?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any harm in, is there any downside to not looking at the id?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconsciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In politics, people specialize in not looking at the id.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In politics, malice, fraud, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay just as long as you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the more sophisticated person wants to know, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ask yourself what does mankind generally want to admit about itself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and then project it onto others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So the value of understanding the id
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is you see what people do not want to admit about themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and they therefore project it onto others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So all the evil that they see everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:15:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is generally a projection of their own hatred, hostilities, fears, jealousies, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So in psychoanalysis you become familiar with the id.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The id is all that is forbidden and repressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the deepest things hidden is the death instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Death instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud said there's eros and thanatos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eros is the basic instinct of life and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanatos is the basic attraction of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And certainly at the guillotine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,15,000 died in the guillotine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And throngs by the hundreds of thousands witnessed the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The death instinct, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I listen to you discussing prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I pray morning and evening and sometimes in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always ask the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,may I be a servant of the Lord as part of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Put yourself closer to the mic, see if I can hear you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've asked to be a servant of the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So anything that shows up in my world that day is mine for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I have asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I've got a tremendous amount of pain, like physical pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's not gone away with, say, treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,or I've tried...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried to disappear it according to your tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, would I be right in assuming that this is karmic and possibly I've caused pain to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is, I have pain and I just pray to forgive myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to have forgiveness for having caused pain to others and just suffer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Like just, I have to live, like the pain just has to be felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is an option at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Later on, you can let go, experiencing the pain itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you quit resisting it, eventually it will run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain only lasts so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you quit resisting it, and eventually it runs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When you've run out that, you know, Estes used to call it a stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When that stack is run out, it's run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:18:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, but a certain, what I was wondering is, like, what I said to myself and as part of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,my prayer, since it hasn't gone in other ways, that for some reason I do have to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then you weren't praying if you're willing to resist it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're questioning it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,First you ask for it, then you question it and don't want it when you get it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've got the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll either go away or your awareness of it will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll still be there if you think about it, but you never think about it, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In working with young children like age six or seven, what would you say are some of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the most important things that you've learned in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think it's important to know that you're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you say are the top one or two spiritual practices that are important for
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,supporting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She's working with children that are like six and seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Age group six and seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you say is their top practices that you would advise them to use?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The children to use?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you said the link to happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that first slide he did on the link between happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The link between happiness and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely the link to happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And to get them up to those states.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To get them up to those states.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's six years you don't have to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're already in that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess supporting them to stay in that, I guess trying to do some things to help
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,them stay in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you developed a capacity to be loving and concerned about others, loving concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,about others, also loving towards yourself, and loving towards your parents, and loving
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,towards your classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably the most advanced thing you can learn, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindness, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, children can be nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be really the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sexy to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:20:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would teach you kindness out of anything else and compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can start with animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindness to doggies and kitties and that which is, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of protect itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion for all living things, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And the willingness to help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm, mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendliness, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendliness and willing to, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,if a child falls down, go over and see if they need help
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,or, you know, help them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, six-year-olds, if you teach that at that age,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that that makes them better human beings in the long run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kindergarten, first grade, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Better you than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so my question has to do with the moment of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,With the mode of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Moment of death, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess it's a fear that I'll go to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and wanting to stay awake, you know, when I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you won't want to stay awake when you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you want to hang on to that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a Buddhist teacher before who said that if you don't stay awake
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're dying, that you'll end up back on the karmic wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make any sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know what you're saying, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not aware that you're dying and you go on living
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,not knowing that you're dead, that is a problem, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So can you call out for help from somebody like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,At a time like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can choose to remain conscious through the transition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:22:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, by knowing that death is not a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that can happen is you leave the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're right, a lot of people believe in death
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to such an extreme amount that they'll sometimes go unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,for a couple hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can choose to stay conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can choose to stay conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask God to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget you have helper angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask your guiding angels to help you stay conscious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and to learn from this experience through this transition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.27,0:22:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you die, you're not going to really care about it at all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because the body is laying there, but you're not the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.72,0:22:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's rather irrelevant what's happening to the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.87,0:22:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the body is extremely boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.68,0:22:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dumb looking thing, the idea that you're cherishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You've cherished it to such a degree, it seems like an absurdity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a dumb looking thing laying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:23:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no desire to get back in it, to tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're karmically destined that you have to go back, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But it isn't, you know, you think, well, you would have an aversion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to leaving the body and physical death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, on the contrary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.67,0:23:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.55,0:23:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.03,0:23:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have, I guess, a psychoanalyst question.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If, when going through the process of, you know, working with a therapist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.17,0:23:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,they ask you to drag up your childhood memories and try
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to unearth things that are causing pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.35,0:23:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just want to ask you, or, you know, if you have a therapist, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.38,0:23:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,one of my only advice is what's the best way to deal with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.14,0:23:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the therapist actually ask you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.14,0:23:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually a family member of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.80,0:23:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And they have, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.84,0:24:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, well, in psychoanalysis, you report anything and everything that comes into your
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,mind as it arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't try to categorize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more like a scholarly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.62,0:24:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.86,0:24:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Examination of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.86,0:24:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But that could be a place to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.75,0:24:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A scholarly examination of what your childhood was like, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.31,0:24:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that, of course, will bring up associated memories and feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's the associated interpretation and feelings that you work with in therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.33,0:24:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you were born and graduated from kindergarten at age five is just immaterial.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.09,0:24:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But the events that happened there and the emotions that were left with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.70,0:24:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you try to see a connection between those things in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.05,0:24:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.05,0:24:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have, like, let's say you had an abusive parent, right,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.41,0:24:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is it enough to just experience it or is there a tool, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.03,0:25:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and the family member that I'm talking to or I'm asking about is having a lot of trouble forgiving that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.55,0:25:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They had an abusive mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.55,0:25:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a tool that is just to, you know, the therapist has asked them just to bring it up, right,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.09,0:25:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and just to experience it and experience it like a victim, like as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.05,0:25:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that enough or is this, should we seek help elsewhere, I guess, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.27,0:25:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you bring it up and see the conclusions that you drew about yourself and about life, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.70,0:25:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And you try and compare that to a more sophisticated adult view.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.33,0:25:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.81,0:25:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And to, like, so it's more like re-education, more like re-education.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.13,0:25:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But it may take some working through to re-educate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.55,0:25:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.85,0:25:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To make a mistake doesn't mean that you're worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.05,0:25:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go hide in a closet and kill yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.41,0:25:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.81,0:25:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.39,0:25:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So a more permissive superego, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.29,0:25:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.87,0:26:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.53,0:26:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not necessary to take such an extreme self-punitive view of mistakes and errors.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.57,0:26:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So you become more congenial towards yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.59,0:26:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.70,0:26:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.05,0:26:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.33,0:26:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.27,0:26:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.50,0:26:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you explain the difference between compassion towards someone and enabling so that I can make sure that I'm not getting in the way of someone's karmic undoing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.50,0:26:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion means accepting that that's part of the human potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.05,0:26:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion means accepting that that's part of the human potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.29,0:26:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And compared to what was the second, compared to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.33,0:26:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Enabling.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.98,0:26:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Enabling.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.59,0:26:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, enabling.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.79,0:27:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, enabling means to assist the other person in that behavior, to assist, to contribute to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.29,0:27:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If their problem is they're feeling sorry for themselves, an enabler would say, oh, poor so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.50,0:27:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you did have a terrible time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.31,0:27:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, potentiate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.74,0:27:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of trying to get the person to see that that's, that what happened at that time for what could be learned from it at that time, but now is a different time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.31,0:27:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And, therefore, we have to grow beyond these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.75,0:27:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Enabling means you assist the person with excuses for, to continue pathologic behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.51,0:27:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the classic example is the alcoholic whose spouse, you know, makes excuses for him, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.90,0:27:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So they take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.74,0:27:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So it would be a matter of taking responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.12,0:27:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not enabling if you insist that the other person take responsibility for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.05,0:27:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.50,0:27:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So they're not playing victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.00,0:28:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.70,0:28:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.68,0:28:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I always feel like I could answer it better than I do, but I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.18,0:28:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,May or may not be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.74,0:28:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.74,0:28:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.74,0:28:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.74,0:28:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In all of the Hawkins materials I've been exposed to and the lectures I've attended, I've only heard you talk about past lives as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.18,0:28:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.18,0:28:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.18,0:28:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.18,0:28:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.18,0:28:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.18,0:28:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.18,0:28:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.18,0:28:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.18,0:28:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.18,0:28:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.18,0:28:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.18,0:28:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.18,0:28:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.18,0:28:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.18,0:28:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.18,0:28:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.18,0:28:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.18,0:28:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.18,0:28:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.18,0:28:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.18,0:28:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.18,0:28:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.18,0:28:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.18,0:28:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.18,0:28:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.18,0:28:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.18,0:28:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.18,0:28:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.18,0:28:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.18,0:28:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.18,0:29:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.18,0:29:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.18,0:29:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.18,0:29:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.18,0:29:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.18,0:29:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.18,0:29:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.18,0:29:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.18,0:29:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.18,0:29:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.18,0:29:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.18,0:29:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.18,0:29:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.18,0:29:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I just, I don't recognize your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.18,0:29:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.18,0:29:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,permission to ask about this I have had feminine lifetimes resist well what do
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.27,0:29:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.40,0:29:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,well well I mean if I was interested in researching it I would it just hasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.18,0:29:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,come up okay well it's pregnant I'd look into it no I don't recall any
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.60,0:29:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,spontaneously that's an interesting question I've never been asked before
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.38,0:29:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've ever looked at it the only ones I consciously recall we're all male
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.42,0:30:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetimes yes thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.18,0:30:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's funny I've never looked at that before hi it's Barack Obama Marxist
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.60,0:30:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Socialist is he a monster social
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.90,0:30:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is he a monster socialist
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.16,0:30:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is he a monster socialist
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.18,0:30:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,he's a socialist he is yeah admittedly he says he's a socialist
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.14,0:30:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but like a Marxist like a seriously Marxist socialist not consciously
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.20,0:30:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Marxist per se no but the Marxian dialectic you have to understand the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.86,0:31:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Marxian dialectic even if you depoliticize it is picturing life as
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.74,0:31:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,perpetrator and victim
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.16,0:31:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you can then project that on everything and anything all minorities thereby
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.01,0:31:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,become victims all all including people who believe in God who live in the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.86,0:31:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,minority in large parts of the world so a picture you know what's your picture
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.16,0:31:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you define then is what you find and what you look for the Marxian
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.58,0:31:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,dialectic is one of perpetrator victim it sees it because it projects it and
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.16,0:31:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the way it projects it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.92,0:31:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two trees, trees in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.80,0:31:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the little tree, here's the big tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.70,0:31:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, the sun comes this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.27,0:31:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so the big tree throws the small tree in the shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.18,0:31:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So a Marxian would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.75,0:31:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,well, the big tree is robbing the small tree
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.10,0:31:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of sunshine and energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.74,0:31:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.46,0:31:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not robbing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.96,0:32:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.44,0:32:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no evil intention behind it, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.62,0:32:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have concerns about...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.34,0:32:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.77,0:32:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have concerns about him becoming president
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.60,0:32:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of the United States of America
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.38,0:32:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the global implications of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.68,0:32:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.64,0:32:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And the global implications of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.01,0:32:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, so is everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.64,0:32:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.75,0:32:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the polls don't show that everybody's concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.01,0:32:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The polls don't show that everybody's concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.94,0:32:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure the polls do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.25,0:32:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you watch Fox News?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.46,0:32:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.44,0:32:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you watch, NBC or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.58,0:32:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I watch Fox News,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.90,0:32:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but the polls still show Obama leading by eight points,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.10,0:32:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and so, you know, it keeps looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.22,0:32:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have they called you for a poll?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.88,0:32:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.36,0:32:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't called me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.62,0:32:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.86,0:32:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so there's hope still.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.22,0:32:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So that tells you right there,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.86,0:32:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think their polls are balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.68,0:32:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.77,0:32:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe polls too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.79,0:32:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but besides, it won't make any difference
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.24,0:33:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because if this person was a Republican,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.42,0:33:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,if this person wins, we move this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.84,0:33:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and if this person wins, we move that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.50,0:33:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.80,0:33:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we go back and forth like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.53,0:33:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In my lifetime, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.56,0:33:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember my father used to get livid about FDR.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.50,0:33:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,FDR was a goddamn socialist and union organizer,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.84,0:33:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's going to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.70,0:33:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for FDR,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.30,0:33:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we probably wouldn't have made it through World War II,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.34,0:33:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, Lend-Lease and all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.80,0:33:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,rebuilt the American economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.53,0:33:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So it depends on how you look at FDR, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.06,0:33:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,these evil, evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.42,0:33:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,evil demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.46,0:33:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,or did he save American society?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.40,0:33:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.66,0:33:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But didn't FDR have the resume of a Barack Obama?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.62,0:33:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't have what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.56,0:33:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't have Barack Obama's resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.10,0:33:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Resume?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.92,0:33:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.32,0:33:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.24,0:33:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Experience, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.64,0:33:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.08,0:33:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a little bit nervous about Barack,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.72,0:33:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but that might just be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.84,0:33:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how do you get experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.62,0:33:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By doing the job, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.01,0:33:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,On-the-job training.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.66,0:33:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.42,0:34:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, all of us are stake-wise on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.14,0:34:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.24,0:34:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all into on-the-job training,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.60,0:34:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and we try to stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.09,0:34:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever's president,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.11,0:34:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we're all going to try to put our shoulder to the wheel
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.98,0:34:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and help that president,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.00,0:34:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,whoever it might be, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.53,0:34:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,because we all,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.44,0:34:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,our survival depends on his doing the best job.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.13,0:34:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So whoever gets to be elected,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.57,0:34:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do the best I can to support that person
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.42,0:34:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and what I consider integrity and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.57,0:34:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.42,0:34:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so prayer would,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.42,0:34:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah, prayer would help, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.40,0:34:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're stating your intention
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.48,0:34:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and adding your intention of integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.36,0:34:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and worthwhileness and reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.42,0:34:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.70,0:34:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.59,0:34:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.24,0:34:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.30,0:34:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.11,0:34:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See, both sides are influenced by the collective intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.65,0:34:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, both sides, not just one side.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.88,0:34:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.46,0:34:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.42,0:35:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just like to wish a blessing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.15,0:35:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.92,0:35:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.39,0:35:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The home of the best and the worst
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.19,0:35:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hope that the best flourishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.31,0:35:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.59,0:35:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.63,0:35:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So my, I'm a little bit nervous presently,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.57,0:35:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,probably because the nature of my inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.07,0:35:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been, spent my life inquiring into the nature of being
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.71,0:35:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know less now than when I began.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.33,0:35:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.67,0:35:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel that I've been very unembodied.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.46,0:35:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've practiced things to embody,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.15,0:35:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,my existence, you know, I've been very fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.05,0:35:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been free from injury and sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.07,0:35:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've found a partner who loved me like a mother
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.73,0:35:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but was unable to bear a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.83,0:35:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to have a child, much like you said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.57,0:35:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,in having a pet to love or another to walk with.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.51,0:35:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted a child to love, to feel more embodied.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.00,0:35:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I left that partner and I joined another and had a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.77,0:36:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, I've been very fortunate, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.03,0:36:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been very fortunate, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.13,0:36:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived with her for three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.96,0:36:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but there was a constant tension and fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.90,0:36:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was difficult to be with a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.53,0:36:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to have that sort of environment for a child to grow up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.44,0:36:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So I left, left them and she returned to her home country
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.07,0:36:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of Austria where the child had an accident
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.92,0:36:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and he suffered a axial, diffuse axial brain trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.17,0:36:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, if it's been anyone older,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.81,0:36:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,he might be still in a coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.01,0:36:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's now a full 100% recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.84,0:36:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to force her to come back to Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.01,0:36:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, and she said she didn't want that imposition made on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.86,0:36:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I granted that she could be wherever she wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.15,0:36:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would travel to support the child there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.25,0:36:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a result, she wants to come to Australia now,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.78,0:36:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,which is great because I want to be around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.25,0:36:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it now means that the mother of my son
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.82,0:36:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and my partner will be living in Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.90,0:37:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're living in the same town.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.16,0:37:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can track this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.59,0:37:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Janine's a social worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.68,0:37:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can help you with this long involved narrative.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.13,0:37:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Essentially, there is this case where there are two women
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.11,0:37:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that I feel caring of living in proximity to each other
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.13,0:37:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and in tension with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.86,0:37:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And my challenge is to live in a way
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.66,0:37:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't properly reflect the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.72,0:37:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.90,0:37:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think I can propagate this tension with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.63,0:37:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you could stop breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.86,0:37:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.94,0:37:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be the cause of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.50,0:37:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around with women's lives is what I advise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.07,0:37:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of cute and it's kind of cheeky.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.48,0:37:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do feel that it is a travesty and it is an offense against women.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.03,0:37:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's uncomfortable for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.80,0:37:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly uncomfortable for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.30,0:37:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just see that women,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.72,0:38:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and the earth as a feminine being,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.82,0:38:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, the feminine has been abused.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.70,0:38:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not something outside of my own life that I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.00,0:38:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.00,0:38:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what the question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.90,0:38:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.90,0:38:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's being put into a position where he has two women
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.80,0:38:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that he cares about in the same town.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.58,0:38:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And he doesn't know how he's going to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.54,0:38:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.68,0:38:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.68,0:38:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're going to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.02,0:38:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.72,0:38:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're going to do a lousy job of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.72,0:38:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done a lousy job so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.72,0:38:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you change?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.72,0:38:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't get any stupider in the situation you got yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.72,0:38:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I would get out like a gentleman,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.72,0:38:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,tell them you've loved them both and bid them fond farewell
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.72,0:38:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave women alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.72,0:38:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.72,0:38:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's great to sit amongst you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.72,0:38:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have a photo taken between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.90,0:38:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.10,0:38:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.32,0:38:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.72,0:39:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a photo taken between you both?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.72,0:39:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.72,0:39:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get friendly with my wife either.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.72,0:39:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be telling her she's a beautiful woman, you son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.72,0:39:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's up to it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.72,0:39:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.72,0:39:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You need another hobby than seduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.72,0:39:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.72,0:39:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep them laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.72,0:39:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.72,0:39:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.72,0:39:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.72,0:39:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.72,0:39:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to ask a question, but now I'm afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.72,0:39:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because of what you said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.72,0:40:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.72,0:40:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.72,0:40:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Firstly, Rom and I are from Australia,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.72,0:40:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just want to thank the both of you for everything that you've given us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.72,0:40:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're from down under Elsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.72,0:40:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.72,0:40:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you don't fall off the planet when you're coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.72,0:40:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.72,0:40:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only because of you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.72,0:40:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just want to thank you both from the bottom of our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.72,0:40:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.72,0:40:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.72,0:40:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it's appropriate, next week we're getting married here in Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.72,0:40:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goody good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.72,0:40:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.72,0:40:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.72,0:40:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.72,0:40:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.72,0:40:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.72,0:40:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.72,0:40:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.72,0:40:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.72,0:40:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're having your students present, or a group of your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.72,0:40:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it would be appropriate to ask for a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.96,0:40:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.96,0:40:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, Sasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.96,0:40:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless your wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.96,0:40:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As a spiritual couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.96,0:40:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.96,0:40:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As a spiritual couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.96,0:40:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, God bless you both as a spiritual couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.96,0:40:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.96,0:40:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.96,0:40:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.96,0:40:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.96,0:40:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.96,0:40:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.96,0:40:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.96,0:40:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.96,0:40:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.96,0:40:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.72,0:41:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.36,0:41:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in Sedona for three years, and it's been a wonderful three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.17,0:41:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think I've just realized that I don't do anything without looking for gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.71,0:41:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think or do anything without looking for gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.31,0:41:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's taken three years for that to really hit home, but it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.01,0:41:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.85,0:41:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you let a thing become what God wills it to be instead of what you will it to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.31,0:41:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to get over your personal willfulness?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.87,0:41:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.94,0:41:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Outcomes to God, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.50,0:42:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And pray for God's guidance and surrender it to God instead of what you think you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.00,0:42:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, you don't know what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.73,0:42:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You just know what you think you want, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.75,0:42:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might clarify what it is you really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.07,0:42:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to find happiness in one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.17,0:42:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find the source of happiness, you don't need anything from out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.17,0:42:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can stop wanting anything to happen or anything to be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.39,0:42:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the source of happiness is within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.71,0:42:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is going to make it happen otherwise, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.31,0:42:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.77,0:42:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.69,0:42:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.00,0:42:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.35,0:42:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking only for knowledge of his will for us and the power to carry it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.17,0:42:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we pray to God for.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.51,0:43:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowledge of his will for us and the power to carry it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.83,0:43:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.41,0:43:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.73,0:43:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.51,0:43:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want a moment of silence with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.17,0:43:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.73,0:43:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.21,0:43:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.53,0:43:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.51,0:43:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.23,0:43:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.17,0:43:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.51,0:43:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a fun animal story and there's a question in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.51,0:43:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I practice a meditation that you had in Eye of the Eye where we radiate love through our body.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.51,0:43:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a little cat that comes and sits on my lap when I do that and she stays perfectly still.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.48,0:43:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she'll move and I'll realize that I'm thinking of something negative and she'll jump down.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.94,0:43:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if I go back to that love state, she's usually gone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.51,0:43:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.01,0:43:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.55,0:43:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So as long as I'm holding that...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.78,0:43:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.19,0:43:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.80,0:43:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.98,0:43:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And she came from a monastery, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.03,0:43:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute karma kitty from a monastery.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.17,0:43:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.03,0:43:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.92,0:44:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So as long as I'm holding a loving...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.07,0:44:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.51,0:44:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right there with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.51,0:44:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.65,0:44:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've gotten better at meditation so I can keep her on my lap for longer periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.88,0:44:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But in my life, if I'm taking a shower, if I'm in the kitchen, a lot of times I'll have
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.78,0:44:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,very negative things come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.01,0:44:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, they're often work-related, like this person did this and I feel this, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.00,0:44:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I might feel victimized or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.23,0:44:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have these...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.40,0:44:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.65,0:44:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And how can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.67,0:44:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm able to do that in that one state.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.46,0:44:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want to get over resentments, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.59,0:44:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.48,0:44:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think you've talked about it today, but if you have any guidance...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.32,0:44:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, letting go of resentments.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.09,0:44:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.30,0:44:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.63,0:44:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the willingness to let go of resentments.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.90,0:44:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's a teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.80,0:44:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't such thing as a justified resentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.00,0:44:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the way you're holding it that makes it look that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.92,0:45:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you let go of holding it anyway, you see that it's just life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.82,0:45:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That car pulled in front of you in the lane, not to get even with you, but because he's
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.74,0:45:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a bum driver or because a rabbit was crossing the road, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.26,0:45:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you stop taking it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.00,0:45:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So the core of the problem is egocentricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.90,0:45:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the things you're happening either for or against or with your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.01,0:45:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.61,0:45:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you stop exerting your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.88,0:45:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, whoever wins the election is whoever wins the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.20,0:45:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.32,0:45:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't give a damn because the one side is going to be as bad as the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.61,0:45:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.76,0:45:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we pray not.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.34,0:45:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.20,0:45:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.70,0:45:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.42,0:45:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to get crooked one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.38,0:45:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.28,0:45:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.70,0:45:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm internally...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.68,0:45:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm putting it on me as if it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.46,0:45:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.88,0:45:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.16,0:45:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.70,0:45:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The egocentricity of it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.80,0:45:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Things just happen of their own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.55,0:45:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.11,0:45:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You just happen to be the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.96,0:46:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So remove yourself as the participant and be merely the witness of the phenomenon of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.53,0:46:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.32,0:46:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.51,0:46:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.03,0:46:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.50,0:46:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whichever side wins is not going to do anything to me personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.84,0:46:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.09,0:46:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.28,0:46:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little harder when it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.82,0:46:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems personal, but I see what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.56,0:46:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems personal, but actually you're just witnessing the phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.76,0:46:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.32,0:46:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.98,0:46:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.90,0:46:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.36,0:46:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.42,0:46:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.72,0:46:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.00,0:46:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.44,0:46:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time I came up here, I was with the question of doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.80,0:46:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.00,0:46:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.28,0:46:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And since then, I've been much less agitated about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.64,0:46:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, one time I was expressing my gratitude to you, and I experienced a level of love
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.46,0:47:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that has remained with me ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.96,0:47:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.38,0:47:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But what I'm asking is some guidance around listening to that still small voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.78,0:47:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Use what?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.70,0:47:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.86,0:47:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Guidance of listening to the...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.38,0:47:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.96,0:47:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Small voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.28,0:47:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Small voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.34,0:47:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.60,0:47:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The intuitive, the...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.90,0:47:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.34,0:47:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.58,0:47:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The guardian angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.36,0:47:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.24,0:47:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could give some advice about how one would set about doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.06,0:47:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.58,0:47:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you ask God for knowledge of his will for you, and you pray for your guardian angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.64,0:47:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has guardian angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.44,0:47:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you ask your angels to make you more conscious and aware of God's will for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.06,0:47:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.46,0:47:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.72,0:47:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's just a matter of...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.28,0:47:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Meditative alignment to become more conscious of God's will for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.10,0:47:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't got any, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.74,0:47:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.90,0:48:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.06,0:48:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that old joke, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.60,0:48:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there's something about you, Horace, that just pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.64,0:48:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.76,0:48:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.54,0:48:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a funny joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.74,0:48:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.80,0:48:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.86,0:48:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.28,0:48:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.84,0:48:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.51,0:48:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.96,0:48:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.76,0:48:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for the way that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.32,0:48:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The many ways that you bless us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.48,0:48:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you for all that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.88,0:48:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My question today is about making good decisions for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.92,0:48:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And personally, I'm being faced with a life-changing decision around my health.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.76,0:48:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I happen to be someone healing from cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.28,0:48:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And my chemotherapy has cleared it 80% to 85%.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.72,0:48:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a trusted doctor saying, you need surgery and radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.48,0:49:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I have very trusted holistic doctors saying, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.78,0:49:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm very torn about how to make the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.84,0:49:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prayed about it, and I just don't seem to get any clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.42,0:49:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep going back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.07,0:49:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you have any insight on how to make the best possible decisions when we're faced
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.79,0:49:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,with some things?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.44,0:49:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.46,0:49:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting two kinds of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.96,0:49:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One is holistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.15,0:49:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.81,0:49:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, holistically.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.27,0:49:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat nuts and wheat germ or something or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.50,0:49:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Vitamin C, IV treatments, mistletoe, ozone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.27,0:49:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.75,0:49:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And Rife machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.27,0:49:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Different holistic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.00,0:49:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's ask something.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.19,0:49:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.51,0:49:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.59,0:49:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.67,0:49:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.71,0:49:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.75,0:49:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.77,0:49:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.84,0:49:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.94,0:49:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.00,0:49:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.05,0:49:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.09,0:49:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.13,0:49:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.15,0:49:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.17,0:49:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.19,0:49:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.21,0:49:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.23,0:49:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.25,0:49:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.27,0:49:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.30,0:49:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The regime that you just explained calibrates over 400, 450, 420.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.38,0:49:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The regime that you just described calibrates at 420.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.60,0:49:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.92,0:50:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Versus what?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.26,0:50:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.16,0:50:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Surgery and radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.16,0:50:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.34,0:50:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.70,0:50:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In your case, surgery and radiation calibrates over 400, 420, 430.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.66,0:50:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.96,0:50:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Go down further.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.76,0:50:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.06,0:50:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,420.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.76,0:50:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,420.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.30,0:50:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,440.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.30,0:50:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,440.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.60,0:50:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,450.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.64,0:50:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,450.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.70,0:50:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,450.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.76,0:50:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In her case, radiation and surgery would offer the best prognosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.06,0:50:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.06,0:50:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.06,0:50:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you crying about?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.06,0:50:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.06,0:50:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.06,0:50:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.06,0:50:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.06,0:50:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I always say the combination of the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.06,0:50:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go the.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.06,0:50:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.06,0:50:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.06,0:50:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.06,0:50:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.06,0:50:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.06,0:50:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.06,0:50:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.06,0:50:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.06,0:50:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.06,0:50:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.06,0:50:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.06,0:50:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.06,0:50:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.05,0:50:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.05,0:50:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.05,0:50:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.05,0:50:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The one.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.05,0:50:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The other is the traditional medical route and add everything else that you can add,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.05,0:50:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, wheat germ therapy and what have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.05,0:50:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.05,0:50:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.05,0:50:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.05,0:51:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.05,0:51:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You only love me because I got you off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.05,0:51:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.55,0:51:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.75,0:51:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.75,0:51:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.05,0:51:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about holistic is it's sort of iffy, you know, in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.57,0:51:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.61,0:51:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.03,0:51:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for sharing, too, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.27,0:51:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, all my questions are generally answered long before I get here,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.96,0:51:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but I do have one concern that's been coming up in my daily meditations, contemplations,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.07,0:51:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and even though I'll get a breakthrough and things are really good almost immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.80,0:51:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel much better and there's a knowingness that you moved on,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.09,0:52:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then almost immediately as you talk about the stack that comes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.38,0:52:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been getting darker and darker.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.96,0:52:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of hairy, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.13,0:52:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Darker and darker?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.65,0:52:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.19,0:52:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we call you a killer or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.13,0:52:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.61,0:52:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Homicidal maniac?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.15,0:52:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.65,0:52:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.88,0:52:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.86,0:52:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanatos.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.05,0:52:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have this contrast of something very beautiful happening on one side,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.36,0:52:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but then the next stack is so ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.96,0:52:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Freud said there's thanatos and eros.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.01,0:52:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eros is the love and life instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.46,0:52:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanatos.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.96,0:52:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanatos is the death instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.65,0:52:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And if eros wins, you live, and if thanatos wins, you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.76,0:52:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.55,0:52:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.03,0:52:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.72,0:53:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So just continue with the surrender, praying and contemplating, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.59,0:53:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're doing all the right things, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.42,0:53:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you become acquainted with the it, but don't forget the it is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.96,0:53:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.42,0:53:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a psychological basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.32,0:53:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's helpful, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.32,0:53:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If the it reigned, there wouldn't be anybody alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.03,0:53:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We would have all killed each other a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.92,0:53:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.09,0:53:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It reigns in certain parts of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.76,0:53:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,People will adopt a political ideology by which 10 million people die of starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.40,0:53:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,10 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.26,0:53:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In another country, they adopted the same thing, and 100 million died of starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.16,0:53:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.46,0:53:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine a political ideology by which 10 or 100 million people die of starvation?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.50,0:53:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And it still has its champions out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.30,0:54:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Its champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.46,0:54:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.46,0:54:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.46,0:54:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.46,0:54:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.96,0:54:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.16,0:54:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.22,0:54:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.26,0:54:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.56,0:54:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Socialism, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.12,0:54:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Brings about death of the millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.16,0:54:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So as the next level just comes up, just to stay here and surrender it, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.68,0:54:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you see how the it is constructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.08,0:54:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You see why things are repressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.04,0:54:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you can see the value of that is because when you see what's repressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.78,0:54:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you then become aware how you project it onto the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.22,0:54:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So the value of unearthing the characteristics of the id is that you see how that gets projected
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.12,0:54:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,onto the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.12,0:54:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me that's evil, it's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.12,0:54:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the evil ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.58,0:54:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, evil is harbored within the unconscious and the id and everyone, you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.08,0:54:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,know?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.08,0:54:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We just call it evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.08,0:55:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The id calls it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.08,0:55:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The id calls it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.08,0:55:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The id calls it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.08,0:55:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The id calls it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.08,0:55:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The id calls it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.07,0:55:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The id calls it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.07,0:55:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it evil or good?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.07,0:55:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was right in me that I could be that.
