Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.53,1:04:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what you're suffering from is hysteria, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.30,1:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're suffering from hysteria, an emotional condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.61,1:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not losing control of your muscles
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.17,1:05:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,or you wouldn't be sitting up here,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.42,1:05:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd be laying on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.96,1:05:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm losing control of my eye muscles.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.88,1:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they do, turn backwards in your skull?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.00,1:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they have to close.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.42,1:05:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They get weak and I can't use them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.51,1:05:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What, your lid muscles?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.01,1:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.86,1:05:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean your eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.69,1:05:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hold your eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.53,1:05:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hold your eyelids up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.59,1:05:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.44,1:05:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.27,1:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.90,1:05:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The eyelid business is emotional.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.65,1:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The eyelid business is emotional, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.77,1:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The eyelid problem is myasthenia gravis, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.34,1:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're seeing a doctor who's doing diagnostic testing?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.90,1:05:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they say about myasthenia gravis?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.40,1:05:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He said the blood work came back negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.48,1:05:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He said what?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.32,1:05:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood work came back negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.07,1:05:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What came back negative?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.17,1:05:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood work on it came back negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.27,1:05:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the blood work.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.90,1:06:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, the blood work just hasn't shown it up yet,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.59,1:06:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.67,1:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She has early myasthenia.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.77,1:06:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.09,1:06:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's antidotes for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.19,1:06:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Myasthenia gravis, there's antidotes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.48,1:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a neuro.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.07,1:06:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of you are hormones, but I don't know if that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.23,1:06:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's antidotes to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.23,1:06:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a neurological problem, a neurologist problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.23,1:06:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.23,1:06:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.23,1:06:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.23,1:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.23,1:06:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I had a number of questions, but they've dissolved on the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.23,1:06:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I really was, it's a very basic question, but when you two were talking together, you
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.23,1:06:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,talked about the recession.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.23,1:06:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.68,1:06:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know here that consciousness is very high, and you were saying that we'd have to
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.80,1:07:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,give up caviar sandwiches and have peanut butter sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.84,1:07:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But one of my daughter's friends, he's lost his job, he's now redundant, and we have other
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.72,1:07:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,friends who are losing their home.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.36,1:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just wondering how we can give them spiritual help or advice, or how do we relate
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.44,1:07:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to them?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.44,1:07:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.44,1:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we show them compassion and not get caught in their drama?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.88,1:07:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.88,1:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you have to stay detached from them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.00,1:07:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got their own karmic, they have their own karmic pattern to live through.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.55,1:07:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.55,1:07:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.55,1:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you do is allow them to live their life without suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.44,1:07:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.44,1:07:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.44,1:07:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.44,1:07:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.44,1:07:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your advice?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.44,1:07:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, I'm not trying to change it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.44,1:07:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I lived through the depression.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.57,1:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Far worse one than this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.67,1:08:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So would it have been better if I had not lived through the depression?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.70,1:08:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who's to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.48,1:08:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.48,1:08:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can live without money and I can live with money.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.82,1:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It adds more conveniences, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.06,1:08:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can still hitchhike every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.81,1:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.81,1:08:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have to have a car.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.88,1:08:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.88,1:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,every single day for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.90,1:08:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.44,1:08:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice, rain, snow, summer, winter.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.06,1:08:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Every morning, every night for years, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.77,1:08:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you learn from that?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.06,1:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.98,1:08:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-independence, stamina, who knows what the purpose of it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.31,1:08:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Very likely there was no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.56,1:08:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just the way life was in those days, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.73,1:08:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And so if the stock market crashes and people lose houses they can't afford,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.43,1:08:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera, it's neither good nor bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.00,1:09:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the current circumstances, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.23,1:09:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's really impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.26,1:09:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.11,1:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's really impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.15,1:09:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.38,1:09:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.17,1:09:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, you know, the government should look into public housing
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.76,1:09:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of everybody, you know, owning their own home.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.07,1:09:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's the...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.72,1:09:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a little ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.90,1:09:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in medical school, we lived in public housing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.86,1:09:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it was a big apartment building,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.50,1:09:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and for $15 or $20 a month you had your apartment,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.18,1:09:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and you also had to help maintain the place
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.74,1:09:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and do your duty on the list of cleaning the stairs, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.53,1:09:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And it cost far less than putting everybody in that apartment
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.86,1:09:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and building in their own home, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.18,1:09:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.76,1:09:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.15,1:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at a high rise in New York City,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.14,1:09:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,imagine 40 floors of people you're going to have to provide,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.72,1:09:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,an individual home for everybody in every apartment
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.90,1:09:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,all the way down the corridor and all 40 stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.76,1:09:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.42,1:09:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.72,1:09:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.22,1:10:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you try to implement a ridiculous idea,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.03,1:10:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you get is failure, and that's what we found out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.80,1:10:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.46,1:10:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.86,1:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.24,1:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.94,1:10:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.48,1:10:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a patient one time, she lived, I forget what floor it was,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.80,1:10:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,32nd floor or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.24,1:10:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She got mugged.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.27,1:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Six times, coming off the same elevator on the same floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.25,1:10:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.31,1:10:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.65,1:10:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Six times.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.89,1:10:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said to her over and over,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.30,1:10:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,are you going to keep living there?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.11,1:10:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.85,1:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Six times, the same elevator, the same floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.80,1:10:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And did she finally move?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.73,1:10:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.77,1:10:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.84,1:10:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Too painful a memory, I think, every present.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.55,1:10:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.27,1:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She would get mugged every time.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.27,1:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come off the elevator, and some idiot would mug her.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.03,1:10:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.89,1:10:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.39,1:10:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the apartment building was crawling with druggies, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.55,1:11:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the various, what do you call them,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.80,1:11:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,groups fought over who was going to control each building, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.34,1:11:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the various gangs.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.46,1:11:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gangs fought over control of the buildings, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.65,1:11:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and various levels of the various buildings, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.13,1:11:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's many solutions to the man.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.26,1:11:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's housing for our mother,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.69,1:11:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and then having everybody in their own house, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.02,1:11:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,like Levittown, USA.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.57,1:11:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.14,1:11:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.56,1:11:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.34,1:11:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.10,1:11:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.72,1:11:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.03,1:11:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.26,1:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.02,1:11:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am part of that lousy triangle as well, the Australian one.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.98,1:11:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're working through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.90,1:11:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of deep friendship there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.30,1:11:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.98,1:11:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.86,1:11:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.90,1:11:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.65,1:11:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.80,1:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.26,1:11:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.07,1:11:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.65,1:11:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, I'm going to move as fast as I can move.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.56,1:11:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.64,1:12:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They gave me such tough questions, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.14,1:12:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy with all them women, he's got me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.06,1:12:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He had me hung up for 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.98,1:12:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise no women questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.61,1:12:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.32,1:12:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up women.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.14,1:12:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the advice I was going to give.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.98,1:12:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.48,1:12:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I just wanted to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.26,1:12:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just really want to thank you guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.53,1:12:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I listened to your lectures as I have a job as a janitor.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.02,1:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I listened to your lectures and noticed now that cleaning is sort of sometimes
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.68,1:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,like a trigger for a spiritual experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.18,1:12:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I'm really thankful for that because when I was a kid, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.84,1:12:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it was really heck for my mom to get me to clean things.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.68,1:12:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I really want to thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.48,1:12:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a question regarding an experience that I had.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.14,1:12:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.26,1:12:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience involved a person I was in a relationship with saying that she,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.92,1:13:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,she intuited or saw in a vision or psychically me being sexually abused.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.82,1:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And when she, when she said that, it triggered like a,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.26,1:13:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,like a, like a flashback or a memory for me, which was like very, very full body.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.40,1:13:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I felt for, for some days like I was being, like I was being stalked or sort of hunted,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.69,1:13:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, to extent, but I, I investigated it like within my family network.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.84,1:13:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've done some past life work and a few other things.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.14,1:13:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.26,1:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Various, various therapists.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.72,1:13:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.28,1:13:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.76,1:13:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I, I don't have a, I guess, I'm, the thing I'm looking for is, is, is whether that,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.42,1:14:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that experience was actually a, a reality or it was something that was put forward on me
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.02,1:14:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,or it was a trigger from a, a past life or, or if.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.84,1:14:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about a memory?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.42,1:14:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, I, I guess my question is if it was something from,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.26,1:14:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,this lifetime as I think it's a fantasy
