Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.60,1:25:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is you know grandiosity
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.68,1:25:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you're in a such thing
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.76,1:25:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,things are what they are
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.84,1:26:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not what you think they are
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.15,1:26:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,think them to be
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.60,1:26:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,or how you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.18,1:26:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,intellectualize it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.80,1:26:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.57,1:26:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.43,1:26:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.88,1:26:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.10,1:26:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,has future applied to the narrative
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.00,1:26:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,not to the reality
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.53,1:26:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.38,1:26:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you bet
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.31,1:26:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.47,1:26:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,same one
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.57,1:26:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a question about an event that occurred in my life,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.76,1:26:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that I perceived that occurred in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.96,1:26:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.11,1:26:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was out on a bike ride a few years ago and was hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.55,1:26:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.30,1:26:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He was hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.10,1:26:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit by a car, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.97,1:27:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And it just so happened you were in Colorado, where I live,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.81,1:27:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that same evening giving a talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.88,1:27:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to talk about coincidence
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.19,1:27:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and, let's see, and accidents.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.11,1:27:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say that there are no accidents.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.05,1:27:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not sure that I would have met you
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.01,1:27:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,if I wasn't involved in that accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.96,1:27:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I have to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.72,1:27:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.23,1:27:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.30,1:27:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I said, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.42,1:27:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you were speaking in Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.19,1:27:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.34,1:27:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.07,1:27:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.77,1:27:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That same evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.31,1:27:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.26,1:27:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was with.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.77,1:27:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In the lecture?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.81,1:27:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.67,1:27:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You missed the lecture?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.55,1:27:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.27,1:27:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.19,1:27:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's not punishment for not being there, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.09,1:27:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that when?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.22,1:27:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was at the Mile High Church.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.63,1:27:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.39,1:27:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.23,1:27:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.93,1:27:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.05,1:28:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We spoke a couple times in Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.27,1:28:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.07,1:28:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.43,1:28:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's a sophisticated question having to do with nonlinear dynamics.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.19,1:28:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, we're talking about, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.19,1:28:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the likelihood of a thing, you know, reaching the 26th decimal point, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.19,1:28:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Iteration means that often when you repeat a thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.22,1:28:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden something completely unexpected will occur.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.13,1:28:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of 10,000 generations of orange fruit flies,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.43,1:28:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden you'll get black ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.09,1:28:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,10,000 times orange, 10,001 a black fruit fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.35,1:28:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.31,1:28:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.03,1:28:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.14,1:28:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.14,1:28:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.14,1:28:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.14,1:28:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.14,1:28:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.14,1:28:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.14,1:28:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.14,1:28:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.14,1:28:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.14,1:28:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.14,1:28:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.14,1:28:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might say part of creation is randomness and the mechanism is discouraged as nonlinear
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.14,1:28:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,dynamics.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.14,1:28:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of 1,000 fruit flies of one color, you'll suddenly get a black one.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.84,1:28:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has no ancestry are black fruit flies.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.32,1:29:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you explain that logically?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.90,1:29:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.90,1:29:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.90,1:29:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.90,1:29:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the fun of it
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.62,1:29:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,no you can't explain it
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.66,1:29:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,no sense in looking for explanation
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.70,1:29:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.20,1:29:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,there are still mysteries of life
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.50,1:29:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,mysteries of life
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.46,1:29:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,mysteries of life
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.64,1:29:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,where does the one millionth
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.38,1:29:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,black fruit fly come from
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.18,1:29:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite field of possibility
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.30,1:29:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,because possibility is
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.24,1:29:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,unlimited it's infinite
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.74,1:29:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.34,1:29:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.10,1:29:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one of those people at the edge of the swamp
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.30,1:29:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know you spoke before
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.07,1:29:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,once about attention and
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.90,1:29:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,decision and effort
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.11,1:29:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was hanging on
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.07,1:29:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the edge of going forward and
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.96,1:30:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,checking calibration
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.86,1:30:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have all the intention in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.48,1:30:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but the decision and the effort is
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.15,1:30:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's a lot of other things
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.30,1:30:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,behind it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.94,1:30:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but do I have to have a better understanding
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.42,1:30:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of the personal will
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.52,1:30:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,just like one would have a better understanding
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.44,1:30:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of the ego to transcend it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.84,1:30:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,do you have to understand that
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.11,1:30:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,well it's more a decision rather than will
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.15,1:30:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't a matter of willpower
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.72,1:30:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a matter of decision
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.30,1:30:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to choose this
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.00,1:30:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,choose this
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.94,1:30:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's a matter of choice and options
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.34,1:30:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.26,1:30:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,presented with options
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.86,1:30:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,continuously
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.30,1:30:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the human
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.36,1:30:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,psyche is
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.30,1:30:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't have any choice
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.73,1:30:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,except to make choices
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.69,1:30:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,all it can do really is make choices
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.30,1:30:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that's really all the mind can do
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.06,1:30:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,when you think about it
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.06,1:30:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is it this or is it that
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.15,1:30:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to make a choice
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.60,1:31:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,every intersection you have to choose
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.14,1:31:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,left or right or straight ahead
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.56,1:31:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,slow down or speed up
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.76,1:31:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you know and again
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.30,1:31:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have any option
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.14,1:31:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,any freedom about that
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.46,1:31:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so this business about freedom
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.96,1:31:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you know is sort of a fantasy
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.36,1:31:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have any freedom at all
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.36,1:31:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,hey you don't have to be moaning any loss
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.68,1:31:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because you never had it in the first place
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.10,1:31:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you're forced
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.96,1:31:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you're forced
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.23,1:31:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the human will is forced
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.73,1:31:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to constantly make a choice
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.65,1:31:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what should the next word be
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.48,1:31:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,what should my inflection be
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.30,1:31:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.11,1:31:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah I do
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.02,1:31:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've been making
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.06,1:31:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what should the posture be
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.11,1:31:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,not to make a choice
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.96,1:31:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what should the posture be
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.23,1:31:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,what you know
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.86,1:31:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have any option
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.40,1:31:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,other than to constantly make choices
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.52,1:31:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so all the human will
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.00,1:31:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the will is constantly making choices
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.86,1:31:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,this and that that
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.02,1:31:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,this and that that
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.94,1:32:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's driven by non-linear gears
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.88,1:32:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.40,1:32:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's really
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.23,1:32:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,really
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.40,1:32:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,really
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.50,1:32:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,really
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.60,1:32:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,really
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.30,1:32:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is really
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.86,1:32:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,fields of dominance
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.64,1:32:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,karmically
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.60,1:32:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a powerful field of dominance
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.61,1:32:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,within that
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.48,1:32:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there are lesser fields
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.68,1:32:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of lesser dominance
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.76,1:32:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,within that
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.40,1:32:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,there's lesser fields
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.36,1:32:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and what we fantasize as freedom
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.77,1:32:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is at the end of the line
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.98,1:32:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,after about 150 decisions
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.80,1:32:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,have already been made
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.77,1:32:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and we call that freedom of the will
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.64,1:32:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,well that makes us happy
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.73,1:32:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to think we have freedom of the will
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.14,1:32:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't have freedom of the will
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.52,1:32:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.98,1:32:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.22,1:32:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.30,1:32:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to grieve losing it
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.96,1:32:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because you never had it in the first place
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.53,1:32:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's what I had the problem with
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.10,1:32:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because you would say that
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.15,1:32:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is what it is
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.72,1:32:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,or people are who they are
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.15,1:32:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but then at the same time
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.42,1:32:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you're like of course
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.18,1:32:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we are here karmically to
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.03,1:32:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that's right
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.88,1:32:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you constantly have to choose
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.82,1:32:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you constantly have to choose
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.22,1:32:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like the rudder of the canoe
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.60,1:33:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the rudder
