Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.27,1:33:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have any choice
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.69,1:33:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have any choice
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.30,1:33:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to have that paddle somewhere
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.50,1:33:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you put it this way
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.14,1:33:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you go this way
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.77,1:33:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you put it this way
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.40,1:33:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you go this way
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.03,1:33:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't have any choice
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.06,1:33:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.27,1:33:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.34,1:33:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,be nice if God
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.42,1:33:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,would just paddle our canoe for us
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.22,1:33:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.80,1:33:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,yep
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.30,1:33:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,, what do you call that system
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.30,1:33:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that tells you where you are
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.40,1:33:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and where you're going
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.80,1:33:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Garmin
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.60,1:33:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Garmin
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.64,1:33:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you need a psychic Garmin
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.14,1:33:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Garmin
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.94,1:33:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I never heard anything so crazy as a Garmin
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.94,1:33:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,until I heard a Garmin
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.94,1:33:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it was unbelievable
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.84,1:33:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.48,1:33:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I said this is spooky
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.77,1:33:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.68,1:34:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so from the standpoint of the absolute
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.30,1:34:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,there was nothing that was said today
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.11,1:34:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,nor is there anything being said now
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.76,1:34:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.56,1:34:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.30,1:34:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing happened either
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.30,1:34:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.80,1:34:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,just the infinite silence
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.38,1:34:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that easy
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.68,1:34:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so this is just taking place right now
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.72,1:34:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.98,1:34:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing actually happening
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.72,1:34:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.02,1:34:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,sounds good to me
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.69,1:34:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,how to
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.86,1:34:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,never mind
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.06,1:34:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,no go ahead
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.06,1:34:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to make that experiential
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.30,1:34:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the practice
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.60,1:34:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that's most attractive to myself
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.50,1:34:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is to do what you've said
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.57,1:34:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,like living in the silence
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.19,1:34:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and just witness it all from the silence
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.19,1:34:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is that
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.88,1:34:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that's true
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.42,1:34:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because while you and I are talking
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.42,1:34:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the major part of this consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.50,1:34:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is silent
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.30,1:34:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and nothing is happening
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.02,1:34:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not deciding anything
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.80,1:34:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not saying anything
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.94,1:34:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or hearing anything
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.82,1:35:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,like the ocean
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.15,1:35:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the ocean goes down
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.00,1:35:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe a couple thousand feet
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.68,1:35:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see the waves on the surface
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.30,1:35:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,surface, but there are thousands of feet below that surface which are utterly still.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.46,1:35:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But the mind is looking for justification for its existence, so it focuses on the waves
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.30,1:35:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and says, boy, isn't this some ocean tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.48,1:35:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's the top couple feet of the ocean, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.53,1:35:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The next 5,000 feet down is completely still to the bottom of what you might call a crevasse
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.81,1:35:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever it is across the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.93,1:35:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So thousands of feet down it's still and silent and dark, and the action is only on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.76,1:35:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you could view your own consciousness that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.64,1:35:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only what's going on on the surface that's entertaining, but its reality is far beyond
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.88,1:36:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.38,1:36:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, in today's TV drama, a good thing too, you can't be drowned with every little
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.00,1:36:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,wave that comes along, then we'd all be dead or in the mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.00,1:36:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we've got to move it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.00,1:36:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang out on the bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.00,1:36:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Jeff.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.00,1:36:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Below the surface of the sea, everything is still and silent and peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.22,1:36:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All the action is only on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.65,1:36:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.65,1:36:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What advice would you give those that have committed the eternal sin, or blasphemy, blasphemy,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.65,1:36:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even say the word.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.65,1:36:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.65,1:36:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What advice would you give someone that committed the eternal sin, blasphemy?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.65,1:36:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.65,1:36:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, may I?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.65,1:36:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.65,1:36:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.65,1:36:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
