Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.65,1:37:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That is scary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.65,1:37:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A question like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.65,1:37:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,See, there's other ways to recover other than forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.65,1:37:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the karmic paying it up, paying it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.65,1:37:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.65,1:37:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,paying it off. Well, let's say you curse God, okay? That's blasphemy. And I hear it done
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.13,1:37:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,on certain internet websites that even specialize in blasphemy. They scare the wits out of me
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.73,1:37:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when I read them. You know, that's the one sin for which there is no forgiveness. If
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.26,1:37:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no forgiveness, then what are you going to have to do? You're going to have
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.76,1:38:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to live out your prison term, right? So whatever suffering goes with that, you'll have to go
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.36,1:38:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,through it. You're not going to be relieved of the suffering by forgiveness. Forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.84,1:38:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,really means that you will not suffer for a certain thing, you know. And otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.68,1:38:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just whatever the crime is, if it's 20 years in prison for that, so you serve the
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.98,1:38:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,20 years in prison. If there was forgiveness, they would forgive the 20 years that you're
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.65,1:38:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,out of your mind at the time, mentally ill, not responsible or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.76,1:38:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you were fully conscious and made a decision with your will and agreement and
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.32,1:38:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,your committed blasphemy, which, by the way, calibrates at 10, then you just suffer some
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.65,1:38:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,time in hell. So, big deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.53,1:38:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.30,1:38:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Firstly, we would like to thank you and Susan for all of your works. We very much
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.30,1:38:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.76,1:38:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly, and simply, we'd just like to ask for your blessings.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.52,1:38:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.61,1:39:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.26,1:39:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.86,1:39:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.69,1:39:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.26,1:39:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to give them our blessing. Yeah, we give you our blessing. God bless
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.14,1:39:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.40,1:39:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.07,1:39:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.86,1:39:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.46,1:39:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.92,1:39:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We got to move it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.76,1:39:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I got one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.11,1:39:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.22,1:39:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,One more.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.86,1:39:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.92,1:39:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Last one.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.42,1:39:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on time.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.90,1:39:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.78,1:39:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop, hop, hop, hop, hop, hop.
