Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.78,1:39:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.28,1:39:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.78,1:39:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been coming for about a year now and have taken you as my teacher and...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.44,1:39:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.94,1:39:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've noticed the schedule for your visits for opening to all of us here like you're not
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.03,1:39:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,going to be...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.53,1:39:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only four sessions.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.64,1:39:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Next year.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.64,1:40:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.64,1:40:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even here in Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.64,1:40:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.64,1:40:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean next year?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.64,1:40:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.64,1:40:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.64,1:40:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, next year we're going to do Prescott, I guess, for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.64,1:40:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.64,1:40:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.64,1:40:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Four of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.64,1:40:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.64,1:40:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,More seating.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.64,1:40:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have four seminars and we have so many people that we have to turn away when
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.64,1:40:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we have seminars here in...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.53,1:40:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.53,1:40:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This only seats 350 or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.53,1:40:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They are building a new auditorium at the high school.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.53,1:40:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be done in 2015.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.53,1:40:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.53,1:40:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.53,1:40:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.53,1:40:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be done in 2010.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.53,1:40:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So hopefully, when that's completed, we will return to Sedona and have events there.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.53,1:40:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.53,1:40:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have bigger seating.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.53,1:40:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.53,1:40:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We have more people than what can come in here and every day we get emails, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.53,1:40:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,complaining about we have to do a satellite room when we're in this event.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.53,1:40:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.53,1:40:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is about the only place that we know that would sit close to the amount of people
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.53,1:40:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.53,1:40:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.53,1:40:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking at...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.53,1:40:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go to a larger venue.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.53,1:40:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.53,1:40:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.53,1:40:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
