Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.53,1:40:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.53,1:40:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.53,1:41:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I feel like I haven't learned everything that I need to learn yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.47,1:41:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.47,1:41:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't want to lose you yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.47,1:41:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you won't lose me, I'll be around in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.46,1:41:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.46,1:41:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we hang out, Prescott, Prescott Valley, the worst would be Phoenix, all the way to
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.68,1:41:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.22,1:41:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We hang out in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.47,1:41:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.47,1:41:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.47,1:41:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.47,1:41:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.47,1:41:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We do have dato.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.46,1:41:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.46,1:41:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.34,1:41:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless us, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.14,1:41:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How fortunate we are to be together.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.93,1:41:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How fortunate we are to be with such holy company, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.43,1:41:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and that we're all in one place and all of one intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.22,1:41:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And we strengthen each other by our collective intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.34,1:41:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one of us is more than what we would have been had we been alone
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.81,1:42:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,because we have an effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.52,1:42:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one multiplies the intentional power of the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.81,1:42:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not arithmetic.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.22,1:42:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not arithmetic.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.69,1:42:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a, you know what I'm thinking, God, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.57,1:42:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the word is.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.46,1:42:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So two of us doesn't have twice the power of one.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.26,1:42:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably has three or four times.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.48,1:42:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And three of us has probably 20 times.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.80,1:42:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So we empower each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.15,1:42:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The collective empowerment of a group like this is probably not even measurable, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.68,1:42:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And it transcends time and location.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.11,1:42:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't just go down the road eight and a half miles.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.43,1:43:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an empowerment within the field of human consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.27,1:43:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So a group like this influences the collective.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.09,1:43:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The group like this is influencing favorably the collective,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.14,1:43:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the collective consciousness of all of mankind from now on through the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.11,1:43:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.64,1:43:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Zippity-doo-dah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.26,1:43:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a good thing to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.43,1:43:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to know that the consequence of one life
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.19,1:43:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is to fulfill the spiritual potentiality of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.31,1:43:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So we serve not just ourself and not just our fellow member of this group,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.09,1:43:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but we serve all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.11,1:43:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We serve all of life by our intention and by our collective power.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.31,1:44:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A group like this serves all of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.26,1:44:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.34,1:44:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves all of life, including animal life.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.23,1:44:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.64,1:44:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegetative life.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.69,1:44:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, it serves all of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.97,1:44:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can see places in the planet where life is just florid.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.15,1:44:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is just florid and flowing out from every nook and cranny.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.30,1:44:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Collects a little dust, and out of that grows a vine.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.30,1:44:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of that vine grows some bugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.30,1:44:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of the bug grows some birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.69,1:44:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of the birds grows a cat.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.94,1:44:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of the cat grows a kid who wants a kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.06,1:44:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So life propagates life.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.42,1:44:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to know that by our intention, then, we are aligned in a very powerful way.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.98,1:44:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And that we are, our decision to serve God as best we can,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.30,1:44:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is there is no higher intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.53,1:44:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no higher intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.06,1:45:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the highest intention of which man is capable, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.53,1:45:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that is the highest intention of which man is capable.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.53,1:45:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, it is our desire to serve God.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.90,1:45:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of our desire to do so, we actually are doing so.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.42,1:45:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.30,1:45:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That we are given the opportunity to serve God.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.42,1:45:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And that by our intention, we have aligned ourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.14,1:45:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are serving God.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.68,1:45:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And by doing that, we are also benefiting all of life, including mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.00,1:45:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Including animal kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.46,1:45:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Including all of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.30,1:45:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So we uplift life by our intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.53,1:45:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we become like an arm of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.53,1:45:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.53,1:45:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.53,1:45:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We become effectively an arm of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.77,1:45:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.77,1:45:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.77,1:46:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That took me a while to get over that one.
