Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.61,1:46:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all that is and all that exists is divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.53,1:46:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we are is divinity expressed as mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.07,1:46:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.46,1:46:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We are divinity expressed as mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.38,1:46:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.38,1:46:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.38,1:46:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that will take me a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.61,1:46:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it will take me a while to digest that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.72,1:46:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Digest that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.72,1:46:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.34,1:46:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thank thee, oh Lord, for divine providence that we may serve thee individually and collectively
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.98,1:46:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,now and forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.52,1:46:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This group is forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.61,1:46:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
