Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.85,1:46:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.85,1:46:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.85,1:46:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a group that transcends time.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.85,1:46:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthly, worldly time.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.85,1:46:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And transcends just personal human interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.85,1:46:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It serves something greater than itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.85,1:47:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That which we are is greater than that which we are.
